                <head>165. Minutes of a National Security Council Meeting<note n="1" type="source"
                        xml:id="d165fn1">Source: Reagan Library, Executive Secretariat, <gloss
                            target="#t_NSC_1">NSC</gloss>: Meeting File, <gloss target="#t_NSC_1"
                            >NSC</gloss> 00054 29 June 1982 (1). Secret. Sent to <persName
                            corresp="#p_PJM_1">Poindexter</persName> under a July 13 covering
                        memorandum from <persName corresp="#p_GMA_1">Guhin</persName>. The meeting
                        took place in the Cabinet Room at the White House.</note>
                </head>
